"當Margaret Cunningham於1403年出生在英國蘇格蘭度福利爾吉爾時，她的父親Gilbert de Cunningham133歲，母親Anne133歲。她於1445年與Sir William Stirling, 1st of Keir在英國蘇格蘭結婚。他們至少是1個兒子和1個女兒的父母。她去世於1466年在英國蘇格蘭斯林史爾斯特林享年63歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1403–1466":"1403年–1466年","1400–Male":"1400年–殁","1402–1413":"1402年–1413年","1412–Male":"1412年–殁","1399–1471":"1399年–1471年","1415–Female":"1415年–殁","1435–1503":"1435年–1503年","1270–1292":"1270年–1292年","1270–Female":"1270年–殁","1471":"1471年","1292":"1292年","1270":"1270年","1415":"1415年","1503":"1503年","1403":"1403年","1435":"1435年","1413":"1413年","1402":"1402年","1445":"1445年","1412":"1412年","1466":"1466年","1400":"1400年","1399":"1399年","Dunblane, Perthshire, ScotlandScotland, United Kingdom":"英国苏格兰培爾登布藍","Stirling Castle, Stirlingshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"英国苏格兰斯林史爾斯特林","Keir, Dumfriesshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"英国苏格兰度福利爾吉爾","Scotland":"英国苏格兰","lifeSummary":"当Margaret Cunningham于1403年出生在英国苏格兰度福利爾吉爾时，她的父亲Gilbert de Cunningham133岁，母亲Anne133岁。她于1445年与Sir William Stirling, 1st of Keir在英国苏格兰结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和1个女儿的父母。她去世于1466年在英国苏格兰斯林史爾斯特林享年63岁。"},"hr":{"1403–1466":"1403.–1466.","1400–Male":"1400–preminuo","1402–1413":"1402–1413","1412–Male":"1412–preminuo","1399–1471":"1399–1471","1415–Female":"1415.–preminula","1435–1503":"1435.–1503","1270–1292":"1270–1292","1270–Female":"1270–preminula","1471":"1471","1292":"1292","1270":"1270","1415":"1415.","1503":"1503","1403":"1403.","1435":"1435.","1413":"1413","1402":"1402","1445":"1445.","1412":"1412","1466":"1466.","1400":"1400","1399":"1399","Dunblane, Perthshire, ScotlandScotland, United Kingdom":"Dunblane, Perthshire, Škotska, United Kingdom","Stirling Castle, Stirlingshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Stirling, Stirlingshire, Škotska, United Kingdom","Keir, Dumfriesshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Keir, Dumfriesshire, Škotska, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1403–1466":"1403–1466","1400–Male":"1400–Zesnulý","1402–1413":"1402–1413","1412–Male":"1412–Zesnulý","1399–1471":"1399–1471","1415–Female":"1415–Zes